{"tid":1317074,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盧卡斯莫拉質疑VVD冇人扭得過紀錄","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:09:19.000Z","uid":16659,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e74b43e8e74cb5fa49e2ebb4b78a6470eaa19430","tid":1317074,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"利物浦上季贏得第6次歐聯冠軍，當中守將雲迪積克表現備受讚賞，更有數據指他整季為利物浦上陣未曾被對手扭過，對此熱刺鋒將盧卡斯莫拉表示懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n為紅軍贏得歐聯的VVD，與隊友沙拿及艾利臣被譽為今年金球獎得獎大熱，更有統計指VVD在整季賽事只曾一次被對手扭過，就是去年11月面對德國時被辛尼扭過。<br />\n<br />\n不過盧卡斯莫拉對此充滿質疑︰「我不太肯定，他們說從沒見過人扭過他，但我們認為只要有人過了他，便是一次盤扭，我相信一定有人試過。我對利物浦射入過一球，當時他在我身後。」<br />\n<br />\n「當然他十分出色，有2米高，與利物浦擦出火花，過了一個很好球季成為英超最佳球員，即使全球有很多出色球員，他亦是3位最佳之一。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=9c9df5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"ef0cc0fa8931f8863702e922dac3f123b9b53525","tid":1317074,"uid":87272,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:34:28.000Z","msg":"VVD會自動走開 所以冇人扭得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0904690096438c75d8525e902f8d04daf14493","tid":1317074,"uid":32066,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:36:49.000Z","msg":"原文:<br />\n&ldquo;They say he hasn&rsquo;t been dribbled past since&hellip; whatever. If the guy is past him, it&rsquo;s already a dribble.&rdquo;<br />\n&quot;The guys must have gone past him now. I know I scored a goal against Liverpool, we lost, but I scored against Liverpool and he was left behind. But he&rsquo;s great. He is.&quot;<br />\n咁都算dribble過咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EHGxdM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EHGxdM.gif&h=cd40f6c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de5ee29329c60e9b52d1f93f62b8a86741170ce5","tid":1317074,"uid":40940,"like":5